---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | Sage & Sprout"
  description="Sage & Sprout's privacy policy: what data we collect, how ads work, and your rights."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy', href: '/privacy/' }]}
>
  <div style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.25rem 5rem;">
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-family-display);font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 2rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose sheet" style="padding:2.25rem 2rem;margin-top:1rem;">
      <p><strong>Effective date: June 27, 2026</strong></p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Sage &amp; Sprout ("we," "us," "our") is committed to your privacy.
        This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your choices.
      </p>

      <h2>Data you enter into calculators</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>We do not collect, transmit, or store any data you enter into our calculators.</strong>
        Dates, cycle lengths, weights, and all other inputs are processed entirely in your browser.
        They are never sent to our servers.
        Calculator state may be encoded in your page URL (as query parameters) for shareability —
        that URL is only shared if you explicitly click "Share link."
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use privacy-conscious web analytics to understand which tools are being used and how we
        can improve. Analytics data is aggregated and anonymized and does not include personally
        identifiable information. We do not share raw analytics data with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        We currently display advertising via Google AdSense and/or premium ad network partners.
        These services may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to serve relevant ads.
        You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://optout.aboutads.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Digital Advertising Alliance opt-out</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Advertising cookies are distinct from the health information you enter into our calculators,
        which (as noted above) never leaves your browser.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our own site does not set first-party cookies. Advertising and analytics partners
        may set third-party cookies as described above. You can control cookies through your
        browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect ad functionality.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party links</h2>
      <p>
        Our content links to external websites (medical society guidelines, government health pages).
        We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any information
        from users under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact/">Contact us.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
